{"tid":1609940,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[賽後檢討] 明明之前大家會封門，封黨鐵出口，點解而家冇哂？","createTime":"2019-10-01T15:53:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T16:37:30.000Z","uid":138268,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"65b4618c79b14ebd906a2d545e645eba9f8a5590","tid":1609940,"uid":138268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:53:50.000Z","msg":"星期日政總速龍推門突襲，<br />\n今日黃大仙速龍突襲當又冇咗好多手足，<br />\n鑽石山又係全部人望住個落咗閘既出口等消息乜都唔做，<br />\n先唔講話打狗救人，<br />\n而家叫你擺幾個雜物垃圾桶封住防狗突襲都唔做？<br />\n真係當啲狗次次慢慢推過黎比你一二一二咁走？<br />\n仲要而家黨鐵運狗，<br />\n未必次次路面推，<br />\n大家啲危機意識去哂邊啊diuuuuuuuuu<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">封門！封黨鐵出口</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">封門！封出口</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">封門！封出口</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"4c8983029250c2a4d2962dc62a37417fecc171af","tid":1609940,"uid":138268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:53:58.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"57debb4638c17db2f5894d8238e2de78c0e52df4","tid":1609940,"uid":138268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:54:09.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"5b5e0c8da734ba7cc36874afcfa1a2161caf958f","tid":1609940,"uid":138268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:55:17.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"c96bbc998db8d333b389fa6eda867e482d539adc","tid":1609940,"uid":326017,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:55:23.000Z","msg":"中環全部用鎖鎖哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02f774cc17ee7083d157c48b9704fad19ef17f34","tid":1609940,"uid":138268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:55:27.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"803fa809c36ceca186aea7a7d77a2950182f3b20","tid":1609940,"uid":138268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c96bbc998db8d333b389fa6eda867e482d539adc","tid":1609940,"